= Rich's Organizer for Wine (ROW)

ROW is simple mobile application that categorizes one's personal wine collection.  ROW also cross referenced wines in the database with a market value based on prices listed by merchants across the globe on Wine-Searcher.com.

ROW is a FileMaker based mobile app that requires FileMaker Go to run this app.  FileMaker Go can be downloaded for free at http://www.filemaker.com/products/filemaker-go/


= Requirement
* Android or iPhone
* FileMaker Go
* Wine you have not drink yet


= Future Plan
* Refine UI
  - Adjust for phone and tablet screen size
* Add temperature reading.  Plan to use Arduino as thermometer's base platform.

